I"O<p>To view remote origin:</p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>git remote -v
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>To add a remote origin:</p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>git remote add origin git@github.com:username/repo.git 
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>or
	git remote add origin https://github.com/username/repo.git</p>

<p>To remove origin destination</p>

<div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>git remote rm origin
</code></pre></div></div>
:ET